Q4. Why Step Functions for remediation?
They want to test orchestration thinking.
Benefits:
•	workflow orchestration
•	retries
•	state tracking
•	conditional actions
•	human approval step if needed

•	Step Functions orchestrates the remediation workflow by coordinating multiple steps, handling retries automatically, tracking workflow state, making conditional decisions based on the root cause, and allowing human approval when critical actions are required.

